{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Rom|15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","chapter":15,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":1,"text":"Now we who are strong have an obligation to bear the weaknesses of those without strength, and not to please ourselves.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":2,"text":"Each one of us is to please his neighbor for his good, to build him up.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":3,"text":"For even Christ did not please himself. On the contrary, as it is written, The insults of those who insult you have fallen on me.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":4,"text":"For whatever was written in the past was written for our instruction, so that we may have hope through endurance and through the encouragement from the Scriptures.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":5,"text":"Now may the God who gives endurance and encouragement grant you to live in harmony with one another, according to Christ Jesus,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":6,"text":"so that you may glorify the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ with one mind and one voice.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":7,"text":"Therefore welcome one another, just as Christ also welcomed you, to the glory of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":8,"text":"For I say that Christ became a servant of the circumcised on behalf of God’s truth, to confirm the promises to the fathers,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":9,"text":"and so that Gentiles may glorify God for his mercy. As it is written,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":10,"text":"Again it says, Rejoice, you Gentiles, with his people!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":11,"text":"And again,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":12,"text":"And again, Isaiah says,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":13,"text":"Now may the God of hope fill you with all joy and peace as you believe so that you may overflow with hope by the power of the Holy Spirit.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":14,"text":"My brothers and sisters, I myself am convinced about you that you also are full of goodness, filled with all knowledge, and able to instruct one another.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":15,"text":"Nevertheless, I have written to remind you more boldly on some points because of the grace given me by God","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":16,"text":"to be a minister of Christ Jesus to the Gentiles, serving as a priest of the gospel of God. God’s purpose is that the Gentiles may be an acceptable offering, sanctified by the Holy Spirit.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":17,"text":"Therefore I have reason to boast in Christ Jesus regarding what pertains to God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":18,"text":"For I would not dare say anything except what Christ has accomplished through me by word and deed for the obedience of the Gentiles,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":19,"text":"by the power of miraculous signs and wonders, and by the power of God’s Spirit. As a result, I have fully proclaimed the gospel of Christ from Jerusalem all the way around to Illyricum.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":20,"text":"My aim is to preach the gospel where Christ has not been named, so that I will not build on someone else’s foundation,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":21,"text":"but, as it is written,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":22,"text":"That is why I have been prevented many times from coming to you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":23,"text":"But now I no longer have any work to do in these regions, and I have strongly desired for many years to come to you","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":24,"text":"whenever I travel to Spain. For I hope to see you when I pass through and to be assisted by you for my journey there, once I have first enjoyed your company for a while.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":25,"text":"Right now I am traveling to Jerusalem to serve the saints,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":26,"text":"because Macedonia and Achaia were pleased to make a contribution for the poor among the saints in Jerusalem.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":27,"text":"Yes, they were pleased, and indeed are indebted to them. For if the Gentiles have shared in their spiritual benefits, then they are obligated to minister to them in material needs.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":28,"text":"So when I have finished this and safely delivered the funds to them, I will visit you on the way to Spain.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":29,"text":"I know that when I come to you, I will come in the fullness of the blessing of Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":30,"text":"Now I appeal to you, brothers and sisters, through our Lord Jesus Christ and through the love of the Spirit, to strive together with me in prayers to God on my behalf.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":31,"text":"Pray that I may be rescued from the unbelievers in Judea, that my ministry to Jerusalem may be acceptable to the saints,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:32","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":32,"text":"and that, by God’s will, I may come to you with joy and be refreshed together with you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:33","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":15,"verse":33,"text":"May the God of peace be with all of you. Amen.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","chapter":15,"paragraphStarts":[1,7,10,12,13,14,22,30,33],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Pleasing Others, Not Ourselves"},{"beforeVerse":7,"text":"Glorifying God Together"},{"beforeVerse":14,"text":"From Jerusalem to Illyricum"},{"beforeVerse":22,"text":"Paul’s Travel Plans"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now we who are strong have an obligation to bear the weaknesses of those without strength, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:1","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 6:2","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 5:14","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and not to please ourselves. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 14:1","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":1},{"label":"Gl 6:2","book":"Gal","chapter":6,"verse":2},{"label":"1Th 5:14","book":"1Th","chapter":5,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Each one of us is to please his neighbor for his good, to build him up. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:22","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:24","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:33","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":33,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 13:9","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":9,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 9:22","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":22},{"label":"1Co 10:24","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":24},{"label":"1Co 10:33","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":33},{"label":"2Co 13:9","book":"2Co","chapter":13,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For even Christ did not please himself. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 8:9","book":"2Co","chapter":8,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" On the contrary, as it is written, The insults of those who insult you have fallen on me."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 69:9","book":"Psa","chapter":69,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 69:9","book":"Psa","chapter":69,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 8:9","book":"2Co","chapter":8,"verse":9},{"label":"Ps 69:9","book":"Psa","chapter":69,"verse":9},{"label":"Ps 69:9","book":"Psa","chapter":69,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For whatever was written in the past was written for our instruction, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:23","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":23,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 3:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that we may have hope through endurance and through the encouragement from the Scriptures. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 4:23","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":23},{"label":"2Tm 3:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now may the God who gives "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit God of"},{"kind":"text","text":" endurance and encouragement "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 1:3","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" grant you to live in harmony with one another, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:16","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to Christ Jesus, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 1:3","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Rm 12:16","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit God of"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that you may glorify the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:6","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" with one mind and one voice."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rv 1:6","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore welcome one another, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:1","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" just as "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or because"},{"kind":"text","text":" Christ also welcomed you, to the glory of God. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 14:1","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or because"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I say that Christ became a servant of the circumcised "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"The Jews"},{"kind":"text","text":" on behalf of God’s truth, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 15:24","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":24,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:26","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to confirm the promises to the fathers, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:16","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 1:20","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 15:24","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":24},{"label":"Ac 3:26","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":26},{"label":"Rm 4:16","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":16},{"label":"2Co 1:20","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"The Jews"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and so that Gentiles "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:29","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":29,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:30","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" may glorify God for his mercy. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 9:8","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" As it is written,"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 3:29","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":29},{"label":"Rm 11:30","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":30},{"label":"Mt 9:8","book":"Mat","chapter":9,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Again it says, Rejoice, you Gentiles, with his people!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:43","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":43,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:43","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":43,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 32:43","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":43},{"label":"Dt 32:43","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":43}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And again,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And again, Isaiah says,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now may the God of hope fill you with all joy and peace as you believe "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 14:17","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that you may overflow with hope by the power of the Holy Spirit. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 2:4","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:5","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 14:17","book":"Rom","chapter":14,"verse":17},{"label":"1Co 2:4","book":"1Co","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"1Th 1:5","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"My brothers and sisters, I myself am convinced about you that you also are full of goodness, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:9","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 1:11","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" filled with all knowledge, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:5","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 8:1","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 8:7","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 8:10","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":10,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 12:8","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":8,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 13:2","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" and able to instruct one another. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 5:9","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":9},{"label":"2Th 1:11","book":"2Th","chapter":1,"verse":11},{"label":"1Co 1:5","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"1Co 8:1","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 8:7","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":7},{"label":"1Co 8:10","book":"1Co","chapter":8,"verse":10},{"label":"1Co 12:8","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":8},{"label":"1Co 13:2","book":"1Co","chapter":13,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Nevertheless, I have written to remind you more boldly on some points "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add brothers"},{"kind":"text","text":" because of the grace given me by God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:3","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 12:3","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add brothers"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"to be a minister of Christ Jesus to the Gentiles, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 11:13","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" serving as a priest of the gospel of God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:1","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" God’s purpose is that the Gentiles may be an acceptable offering, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 12:1","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 2:17","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" sanctified by the Holy Spirit. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15},{"label":"Rm 11:13","book":"Rom","chapter":11,"verse":13},{"label":"Rm 1:1","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Rm 12:1","book":"Rom","chapter":12,"verse":1},{"label":"Eph 5:2","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":2},{"label":"Php 2:17","book":"Php","chapter":2,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore I have reason to boast in Christ Jesus "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:3","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" regarding what pertains to God. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:17","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":17,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 5:1","book":"Heb","chapter":5,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Php 3:3","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"Heb 2:17","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":17},{"label":"Heb 5:1","book":"Heb","chapter":5,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I would not dare say anything except what Christ has accomplished through me "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:12","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 21:19","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:5","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 3:5","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":5,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" by word and deed for the obedience of the Gentiles, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 15:12","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":12},{"label":"Ac 21:19","book":"Act","chapter":21,"verse":19},{"label":"Rm 1:5","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":5},{"label":"2Co 3:5","book":"2Co","chapter":3,"verse":5}],"