s it is written,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"That is why I have been prevented many times from coming to you. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:13","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:18","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 1:13","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":13},{"label":"1Th 2:18","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But now I no longer have any work to do in these regions, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit now, having no longer a place in these parts"},{"kind":"text","text":" and I have strongly desired for many years to come to you "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 19:21","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:10","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 19:21","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":21},{"label":"Rm 1:10","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit now, having no longer a place in these parts"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:15:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"whenever I travel to Spain. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add I will come to you."},{"kind":"text","text":" For I hope to see you when I pass through and to be assisted by you for my journey there, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 15:3","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" once I have first enjoyed your company "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 1:12","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for a while. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 15:3","book":"Act","chapter":15,"verse":3},{"label":"Rm 1:12","book":"Rom","chapter":1,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"te